      "comment_id" : 140648467,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "<code>javac</code> ignores this error as well, which is a confirmed bug. Some tools follow <code>javac</code> rather than the Java language specification. For details see: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/53824670/6505250\">stackoverflow.com/a/53824670/6505250</a>"
